      <title>印度名人索娜姆·卡普尔以 570 万美元收购孟买标志性音乐商店</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/bollywood-star-sonam-kapoor-and-husband-buy-music-store-rhythm-house-in-mumbai</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Bhaane 集团由名人索娜姆·卡普尔 (Sonam Kapoor) 和她的丈夫阿南德·阿胡加 (Anand Ahuja) 所有，该集团将以 4.784 亿卢比（570 万美元）收购印度金融之都孟买的标志性音乐商店 Rhythm House。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/bollywood-star-sonam-kapoor-and-husband-buy-music-store-rhythm-house-in-mumbai</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 09:29:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
