      <title>俄罗斯小麦产量因干旱连续第三年减产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/russian-wheat-crop-seen-shrinking-for-third-year-on-dry-weather</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于降雨不足，俄罗斯这个全球最大小麦种植国的播种推迟，该国小麦产量预计将连续第三年下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/russian-wheat-crop-seen-shrinking-for-third-year-on-dry-weather</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 08:41:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
